This paper presents an ontology-based model for AI-assisted medicine side-effect prediction, which involves the use of artificial intelligence and data mining techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CY (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics).
